reviewText: Excellent source for a very complicated digital SLR.

This helped me with some of the specific features and settings for my newly purchased D750.  I am an experienced DSLR user but was looking for a few specific settings for this model and this DVD was very helpful.
The Nikon D750 is a very complex camera.  It is good that they walk you through step by step
very informative on getting to become familiar with the camera and the advanced controls.
I need add Closed captions Please.
great tips!  Handy to have around.
